樓上都係，紙巾、煙頭同有料M巾都有。"},{"pid":"6c5072f25d21d4ad0a79e5c3c1870dafcc2027c1","tid":749712,"uid":146435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7aa55c92b4027a3157080e055f80ff9e9dccaf76","tid":749712,"uid":45645,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T09:15:04.000Z","msg":"公屋最多仆街"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T11:28:14.000Z","msg":"係大埔多仆街 多怪人"},{"pid":"6794a33adb7ab77a0e8fef0c12134c354452da38","tid":749712,"uid":52056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T15:10:01.000Z","msg":"支那人好鍾意搣咗張M巾就咁掉落垃圾筒(如果有公德到掉落垃圾筒嘅話)<br />\n大大張浸哂血包都唔包吓，陣閪血味未入到廁格就攻哂入鼻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前大學宿舍廁所嘅交流生係咁，返工地方借廁所嘅支那地產客又係咁，就連出入高檔商場掃名牌手袋嘅支那土豪都係咁<br />\n習慣嚟"},{"pid":"c99f62f3f89bf4ca5de7cec4c1b1d9aa95eea6e1","tid":749712,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T15:15:26.000Z","msg":"公屋人唔只窮"},{"pid":"23ffc0447ab54e15cffd524dbe58d75f6c0b0ef8","tid":749712,"uid":52056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T15:15:38.000Z","msg":"呢單新聞掉護墊已經算好彩，以前住宿舍見過成張特長夜用打開哂喺個垃圾筒，仲要係吸哂隔夜血嗰種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db9d63140d201c98bb20e435657b7a380653d24d","tid":749712,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T15:15:53.000Z","msg":"太和邨？"}]}